====修改标题及概要的质疑====

2008年7月22日，8号提案的支持者发动了一项法律疑议，质疑总检察长布朗对投票标题及概要的修改插入了“煽动性”语言，会造成“过度偏见的投票人反对”8号提案。<ref name="mercnewssummary">{{cite news|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_10034736?nclick_check=1|title=Prop. 8 supporters sue over gay marriage ballot language|last=Swift|first=Mike|date=2008-07-29|work=Mercury News|publisher=MediaNews Group|accessdate=2008-08-07|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181410/http://www.mercurynews.com/ci_10034736?nclick_check=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>支持者宣称调查显示总检察长在过去五十年的投票标准中从未使用过像“排除”这样的主动性[[动词|动词]]。<ref name="CNS citation">{{cite news|url=http://www.catholicnewsagency.com/new.php?n=13415|title=Lawsuit filed to challenge California ballot’s ‘inflammatory’ rewording of marriage amendment|date=2008-08-01|work=CNA|publisher=Catholic News Agency|accessdate=2008-10-16|archive-date=2009-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090214114326/http://www.catholicnewsagency.com/new.php?n=13415|dead-url=no}}</ref> 总检察长的代表举出12个用了“排除”这个词的投票标准的案例，并保证投票措辞是[[中立|中立]]且正确的。<ref name="azcentralsummary">{{cite news|url=http://www.azcentral.com/news/articles/2008/07/28/20080728gaymarriagecalif0728-ON.html|title=Gay marriage foes challenge ballot wording|last=Garrison|first=Jessica|date=2008-07-28|work=AZ Central.com|accessdate=2008-08-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogcabinca.org/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/A.G.%20RJN.pdf |title=REQUEST FOR JUDICIAL NOTICE IN SUPPORT OF OPPOSITION TO PETITION FOR WRIT OF MANDATE |publisher=Attorney General of the State of California |date=2008-08-04 |accessdate=2008-11-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327045034/http://blogcabinca.org/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/A.G.%20RJN.pdf |archivedate=2009-03-27 }}</ref>

2008年8月8日，加州高级法院驳回了法律质疑，肯定了新的标题及概要，并指出“标题与概要并非不真实或者有误导性的，因为8号提案将要在加州‘排除同性伴侣婚姻权利’。而加州最高法院正在加州宪法框架下，明白无误的保护同性伴侣的拥有宪法赋予的婚姻权利。”<ref name='sfgatetitleupheld'>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2008/08/08/BAE5127O2F.DTL&type=politics|title=Judge refuses to order change in Prop. 8 title|last=Egelko|first=Bob|date=2008-08-08|work=Sfgate.com|accessdate=2008-08-08|archive-date=2008-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080916234259/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2008%2F08%2F08%2FBAE5127O2F.DTL&type=politics|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="superiorcourt" /> 同日，8号提案的支持者向州上诉庭提起一项紧急上诉。之后一天上诉庭拒绝了他们的[[上诉|上诉]]申请，支持者也未要求加州最高法院审查。<ref name="sfgate_appealdrop">{{cite news | first=Bob | last=Egelko | url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2008/08/12/BADU128V6V.DTL&type=politics | title=Prop. 8 backers drop challenge on wording | work=舊金山記事報 | date=2008-08-12 | accessdate=2020-10-02 | archive-date=2012-03-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315055426/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2008%2F08%2F12%2FBADU128V6V.DTL&type=politics | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://appellatecases.courtinfo.ca.gov/search/case/dockets.cfm?dist=3&doc_id=1374371&doc_no=C059606 |title=Order Denying Petition (Case No. C059606) |publisher=California Court of Appeal, 3rd District |date=2008-08-08 |accessdate=2009-01-12 |archive-date=2016-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124004127/http://appellatecases.courtinfo.ca.gov/search/case/dockets.cfm?dist=3&doc_id=1374371&doc_no=C059606 |dead-url=no }}</ref>  关于投票人手册上的投票概要的措辞与争论的法庭行动截止日期是2008年8月11日。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2008/08/12/BADU128V6V.DTL|title=Prop. 8 backers drop challenge on wording|publisher=舊金山記事報|date=2008-08-12|accessdate=2008-10-25|archive-date=2008-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080827082419/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2008%