kcra.com/politics/17943031/detail.html| title=Protests Against Gay-Marriage Ban Continue| accessdate=2008-17-11| publisher=KCRA.com| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306032352/http://www.kcra.com/politics/17943031/detail.html| archivedate=2012-03-06}}</ref>在旧金山，数千人聚集在[[市政厅|市政厅]]前抗议提案并进行了烛光守夜。发表演说表达对8号提案反对意见的有州参议员马克·莱诺（Mark Leno）及市长加文·纽森。<ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.ktvu.com/politics/17914830/detail.html |title=Thousands Attend Vigil Protesting Passage Of Prop. 8 |publisher=KTVU |date=2008-11-06 |accessdate=2008-11-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081109010730/http://www.ktvu.com/politics/17914830/detail.html |archivedate=2008-11-09 }}</ref>除了在摩门教洛杉矶礼拜堂，抗议也发生在加州其他摩门教礼拜堂外，包括圣迭戈礼拜堂和奥克兰礼拜堂。许多知名人士也加入了抗议，如加州的德鲁·巴里摩尔（Drew Barrymore）<ref>[http://blog.shankbone.org/2008/11/12/drew-barrymore-wikipedia-photo-used-for-no-on-8-article-2.aspx Drew Barrymore to Prop 8 Protesters: I will fight with you] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.shankbone.org/2008/11/12/drew-barrymore-wikipedia-photo-used-for-no-on-8-article-2.aspx |date=20090109110741 }}, DrumChannel.com, November 11, 2008.</ref>和纽约的乌比·戈德堡（Whoopi Goldberg）。<ref name=Towleroad/>

